snippet.title: Touhou 13 - Ten Desires - Ultra Mode 1cc
snippet.description:
Much better.  :V

Ultra Mode is a patch that you can apply to the game. What it basically does is double the amount of bullets, double their speed, both, or something else. This makes for a fun challenge most of the time and sort of gives you a difficulty above lunatic.

There are patches for almost all the Windows games and they can be downloaded here:
http://cheater.seesaa.net/category/9478192-1.html
(Unzip the thxxu.zip in the game folder and patch the Japanese thxx.exe).

Yes, the patch gives you autobombs if you're curious.

New patch came out for 1.00c. Things changed were various patterns, much faster level pacing and much harder overall difficulty.
EDIT:
Scratch that the newest version is almost the same as in the video again.
